17 February 2012Members of the media are invited to the post State of the Nation Address (SoNA) media briefings which will take place on Sunday 19th February and Monday 20th February 2012 as follows: The Justice Crime Prevention and Safety (JCPS) Cluster where the Chairperson and Minister of Justice and Constitutional Development, Jeff Radebe will lead a panel of JCPS Cluster Ministers. Date: Sunday, 19 February 2012 Time: 10h00 Venue: GCIS Auditorium, 1st Floor, Midtown Building, Pretoria The Governance and Administration (G&amp;A) Cluster where the Chairperson and Minister of Home Affairs, Dr Nkosazana Dlamini- Zuma will lead a panel of the G&amp;A Cluster Ministers . Date: Monday, 20 February 2012 Time: 10h00 Venue: GCIS Auditorium, 1st Floor, Midtown Building, Pretoria NB: There will be a video-link for the JCPS and the G&amp;A to Imbizo Media Centre in Parliament, Cape Town Kindly confirm attendance by email or sms to: Shadi Baloyi (Pretoria) E-mail: shadib@gcis.gov.za Cell: 076 946 7136 Loedfie Hendricks (Cape Town) E-mail: loedfieh@gcis.gov.za Cell: 082 670 4145 Enquiries: Mzobanzi Jikazana 083 641 2355 (Pretoria) Cell: 082 413 4609 Liezil Cerf (Cape Town) Cell: 076 778 2380 Issued by: Government Communication and Information System